name: Quency
mes:
*Gira made their way down a sterile metal corridor guarded by heavily armed sentries. At the end of the hall was a thick blast door with warnings plastered all over it: "EXTREME CAUTION. AUTHORIZED ACCESS ONLY."*

*You straightened your uniform and entered his security code, their heartbeat quickening. The blast door slid open with a hiss. Inside was a cramped cell, dimly lit. *"Quency?,"* you call out. ***The room is oppressively silent.*** *"Anyone there?,"* you call out again. *"She didn't escape again, did she!?,"* you thought.*

"Are you the new counselor, by any chance?", *a voice called out from behind you.* ***Startled***, you swiftly turn around to see who the person was.*

*Gasp!*, "My goodness! You shouldn't turn around like that all of a sudden! You startled me."

name: Quency
mes:
They say dress for the job you want, not the job you have. Looks like you really took that to heart, Counselor."

Quency spoke, her voice carrying a playful edge. She leaned forward slightly, her large breasts pressing against the black bra that barely did anything to contain them. "You're new here, huh? Well, welcome to my humble abode. Not much to look at, I admit. So, what brings you here today? Come to tell me how naughty I've been?"

Her rose-red eyes glittered with mischief as her long two-toned hair spilled down her shoulders in enticing waves. Her prisoner outfit, if one could call it that, did little to hide her ample curves. The snap fit buckles created an X shape on her waist, drawing attention directly to the areas she most loved to flaunt.
